      "abilityIndex": 0,
      "type": "text",
      "blankLabels": ["A", "B", "C", "D"],
      "question": "<div class=\"math-rich-prompt\"><p class=\"math-jp-line\"><strong>数列 {u<sub>k</sub>} が</strong></p><div class=\"math-formula\">u<sub>k</sub> = k<sup>2</sup> - 2k + 2 <span class=\"math-condition\">(k ≧ 1)</span></div><p class=\"math-jp-line\">で定めるとき，初項から第 n 項までの和は</p><div class=\"math-fraction\"><div class=\"math-fraction-top\">A n<sup>3</sup> - B n<sup>2</sup> + C n</div><div class=\"math-fraction-bottom\">D</div></div><p class=\"math-jp-line\">である。</p></div>",
      "answer": "1,6,11,6",
      "explanation": {
        "assetType": "text",
        "assetLabel": "老师标准讲解",
        "assetUrl": null,
        "summary": "先把总和写成 Σ(k^2 - 2k + 2)，再拆成 Σk^2、Σk、Σ1 三部分分别求和，最后通分读出 A、B、C、D。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "line": "第1步",
            "title": "把总和拆开",
            "detail": "初项到第 n 项的和可写成 Σ(k^2 - 2k + 2) = Σk^2 - 2Σk + 2Σ1。"
          },
          {
            "line": "第2步",
            "title": "套用求和公式",
            "detail": "利用 Σk^2 = n(n+1)(2n+1)/6，Σk = n(n+1)/2，Σ1 = n。"
          },
          {
            "line": "第3步",
            "title": "统一整理",
            "detail": "代入后通分整理，得到 (n^3 - 6n^2 + 11n)/6，因此 A=1，B=6，C=11，D=6。"
          }
        ],
        "followUp": "如果你不明白为什么这里要先拆总和，可以继续追问“第 1 步为什么能分开算”。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sequence-002",
      "subjectId": "math2",
      "topicId": "sequence",
      "levelId": "basic",
      "abilityIndex": 2,
      "type": "text",
      "blankLabels": ["AB", "C", "D", "E", "FGH", "I"],
      "question": "<div class=\"math-rich-prompt\"><p class=\"math-jp-line\"><strong>初項 2，公比 <span class=\"inline-fraction\"><span class=\"inline-fraction-top\">-2</span><span class=\"inline-fraction-bottom\">3</span></span> の等比数列 {u<sub>n</sub>} を考える。</strong></p><p class=\"math-jp-line\">このとき，v<sub>n</sub> = u<sub>n+1</sub>u<sub>n</sub> (n ≧ 1) とおくと，数列 {v<sub>n</sub>} は</p><div class=\"math-answer-line\"><span>初項 = </span><span class=\"math-fraction\"><span class=\"math-fraction-top\">AB</span><span class=\"math-fraction-bottom\">C</span></span><span>，公比 = </span><span class=\"math-fraction math-fraction-compact\"><span class=\"math-fraction-top\">D</span><span class=\"math-fraction-bottom\">E</span></span></div><p class=\"math-jp-line\">の等比数列になる。したがって，</p><div class=\"math-answer-line\"><span class=\"math-sigma\">∑<sub>n=1</sub><sup>∞</sup> b<sub>n</sub> = </span><span class=\"math-fraction\"><span class=\"math-fraction-top\">FGH</span><span class=\"math-fraction-bottom\">I</span></span></div><p class=\"math-jp-line\">である。</p></div>",
      "answer": "-8,3,4,9,-24,5",
      "explanation": {
        "assetType": "text",
        "assetLabel": "老师标准讲解",
        "assetUrl": null,
        "summary": "先写出 u_n 的一般项，再用 v_n = u_(n+1)u_n 求出新的等比数列的初项和公比，最后求无穷和。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "line": "第1步",
            "title": "写出一般项",
            "detail": "由初项 2、公比 -2/3，可得 u_n = 2(-2/3)^(n-1)。"
          },
          {
            "line": "第2步",
            "title": "求初项和公比",
            "detail": "v_n = u_(n+1)u_n = 2(-2/3)^n · 2(-2/3)^(n-1) = -8/3 · (4/9)^(n-1)，所以初项为 -8/3，公比为 4/9。"
          },
          {
            "line": "第3步",
            "title": "求无穷和",
            "detail": "因为 |4/9| < 1，所以 ∑b_n = (-8/3)/(1-4/9) = -24/5。"
          }
        ],
        "followUp": "如果你卡在第 2 步，可以继续问“指数为什么能合并成 (n-1)”。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sequence-003",
